name: __DataType_Fragment__

                            </element>
                            <element name="objProp2">
                                <simpleType>
                                    <restriction base="double"/>
                                </simpleType>
                            </element>

                    </complexType>
                </element>
                <any maxOccurs="unbounded" minOccurs="0" processContents="skip"/>
            </sequence>
        </complexType>

</schema>
